{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r707327189", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing 3 course meal", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "6 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jaye M", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r707327189-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Went here for a date night via wowcher and it was outstanding! ", "For starter I had the belly pork it was amazing! My partner had the prawns in sauce which she loved, we then had steak for main AMAZING I was so full by this point I couldn\u2019t even eat my desert! Our deal came with a bottle of champagne and it was lovely, the staff were so attentive and couldn\u2019t do more for you! I would definitely go again and I will be, I would highly recommend"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r719028031", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Food and Service", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "17 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "gizmoemmielou", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r719028031-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited on Wednesday 9th October for a Bottomless Brunch deal - \u00a329 pp with 2 hours of Bottomless Prosecco and 3 course Brunch.", "We booked for 1pm but arrived at 12pm, we were told we could be seated early.", "Great welcome on arrival by Jorge, seated quickly and brought the menu - drinks were served straight away and we were left for just under 10 minutes to enjoy the drink and look at the menu. Our drinks were filled and we chose the Eggs Benedict and Bacon Waffles, the Brunch Roast each... I had chicken and my husband the steak and we chose fruit platter and cheesecake for desert.", "Food came quick enough although not immediately which gives the impression it\u2019s cooked fresh. Excellent taste for each course, well presented and good portions.", "Not once throughout our dine did our glass of Prosecco go empty.", "Service from Jorge was exceptional and he was so informative and polite with great humour... he finished his shift at 2pm and we was handed over to a lovely lady server, did not get her name but equally very polite and accommodating.", "Not once did we feel we\u2019d overstayed our welcome and thoroughly enjoyed the experience.", "There were other diners enjoying an afternoon tea which looked equally tasty and everyone seemed to be enjoying the service.", "Keep up the good work, will definitely recommend and we\u2019ll be returning soon.", "Thank you, Emma"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r712637427", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely fabulous meal at the Hilton Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "24 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Pepxinat", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r712637427-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["My family and I booked a Wowcher Deal for under 40 for 2 people with Bubbly. We had a fantastic meal, the Fondant get a special mention as I am not a big dessert person but that was soooooo yummy. Big thumbs to the Hilton Canary Wharf we all had a wonderful time and our waiter was very attentive. Highly recommended and I will be back!!!"]}
