{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r674838839", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sublime food", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "18 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "knowsagoodthing", "reviewer_origin": ["Stratford City, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r674838839-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Had the pleasure of dining here two nights in a row. First night: goats cheese salad - beautiful flavours and perfect presentation. I\u2019d have to deduct a mark or two as it was extremely cold - perhaps had been in the fridge for too long before serving? Some of the cheese, although tasty, was almost icy! I couldn\u2019t fault the steak from the grill. Perfectly rare (as requested) - an utterly delectable delight. Best steak I\u2019ve had in a very long time. ", "Second night: scallops followed by tiger prawns from the grill. Wow! Scallops were incredibly fresh and a total taste sensation. I savoured every mouthful. The tiger prawns were also wonderful. Perfect with the asparagus and garlic butter. Possibly a small bit of fresh crusty bread to mop up the sauce and add a a perhaps needed modicum of carby substance to this otherwise perfect meal. ", "Excellent, attentive service and a quick chat with the chef doing a walkaround was a nice touch. ", "Well done; Hilton - I hope to be back next year to sample these culinary delights again "]}
