{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r670796368", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "EXCELLENT FOOD ! Fantastic service! Highly highly recommended", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "1 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "TheFussyDentist", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "69"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "33"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r670796368-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Ok so I\u2019m sold.", "I spent a night in the hotel a couple of months ago and wrote a bad review!", "I had promised myself I\u2019d never visit again but I had an old voucher for the restaurant which I came across lately and I had to use it of course (who wastes money?)", "So I call up my friend and we turn up for our 6pm reservation.", "First I forget to print the voucher when I had expressly been told to do so!", "The lady on duty smiled sweetly and asked if she could see it on my phone.", "Even worse my phone had died!", "The lady graciously (sorry I didn\u2019t take her name)walked me to the concierge and plugged in my phone and waited patiently for it to charge .", "Five minutes later she verified the voucher and asked where we wanted to sit.", "We picked a table and then we had a look at the menus and placed our orders.", "We were served in total by four different people all gracious, prompt, impeccably well mannered, friendly but unobtrusive and just nice, pleasant happy people, and the meals themselves - heavenly!", "Michelin style presentation and cooked to perfection!", "I have never given five stars on a review and I\u2019ve never wanted to, to be honest,but I truthfully and sadly can\u2019t fault anything today!", "Not the service , not the for food, nor the ambience.", "SO ITS FIVE STARS FROM THE FUSSY DENTIST!", "Well done Hilton Canary Wharf!", "I\u2019m impressed."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r677827629", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Customer Service Very Lacking", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "31 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "abiola92", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r677827629-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here on a wowcher for birthday and I can say I definitely won't be returning. ", "We explained to the gentleman taking our order that our table was even and was causing everything on the table to wobble, (including my champagne which ended up spilling all over the table). He then told us, no one else has complained about this table today and didn't even try and help us fix it. He then said, there are no other tables available in the restaurant, even though there were only 5 other parties dining and there were at least 5 other tables unused. ", "They didn't have half the items on the menu, which wasn't explained until we tried to order, the steak which we ordered medium was hard a rock and the starter was overcooked."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r680744105", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Evening Dinner", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "11 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "aubreyw159", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "205"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "52"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r680744105-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited here with friends and family as part of an online offer option.", "The restaurant was as to be expected within the Hilton Hotel at Canary Wharf.", "Service was initially slow (perhaps we'd arrived at a busy moment) but courteous and attentive. The menu options were very much in keeping with what you'd expect. One of the party chose the red and white house wines from the list which for the price were definitely over priced and just about enjoyable. The food on the other-hand was freshly prepared and well presented. All in all we had a good evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r681839260", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Saturday lunch", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "16 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "753annp", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r681839260-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Very disappointed as I was unable to say anything bad about the visit, the food was cooked to perfection, the drinks beautifully mixed, the staff were helpful and attentive, even the ambience was fabulous. It was so good I may have to use this location for this year\u2019s Christmas dinner, we will need rooms too because if the mundane Saturday lunch was this good can you imagine Christmas?"]}
