{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r651563156", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "DO NOT HERE", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "11 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Omeongag", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r651563156-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["I don't normally write reviews but this is by far the worst customer service I have received and needs to be documented. Firstly the food was not great and not prepared well. The \"supervisor\" is a disgrace to his profession as he ruined the ambience of the experience by constantly standing by our table with discrimination. The blonde waitress who understandably English is not her first language misunderstood the requests made which led to us being overcharged. We saw the supervisor and the waitress debating and came to the conclusion that we were wrong and she was right which led to the supervisor accusing us for lying. He was not impartial and stated due to her being in the role for the year, he trusted her over us. A very bad experience and I advise anyone who is going as a couple not to go. You will have more for your money at a fast food restaurant. Really disappointed with this restaurant. Should be closed"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r646597483", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "60th Birthday let down....", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "17 January 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "baaadad", "reviewer_origin": ["Romford"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "30"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r646597483-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife was given a Buyagift Afternoon tea voucher for her 60th Birthday. We chose to go to the Hilton Canary Wharf as we thought it would be nice to have a view over the docks. The description did say that this was when possible. However we subsequently found out that this has not been an option since early last year. Tea is now provided in the cinnamon restaurant. ", " Now you are seated on the ground floor looking at the main road. To detriment the view further, outside the window are builders fences behind which are the road works, and parked builders vans.", " The afternoon tea itself did not match the image shown in the brochure. The portions were meagre and presentation ordinary. As an example the tea was just a tea bag in a pot, not loose leaf as you would usually expect. Also my wife had to ask for a second cup of tea as this was not offered. The waiter did offer a free glass of sparkling wine to compensate for the lack of view but by then we were already upset. As stated this was a 60th birthday gift for my wife but felt more like popping for tea on the way back from the shops. Very ordinary, not worth the money. Would we come here again, no."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r652706479", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Valentine's afternoon tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "16 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rachaelw954", "reviewer_origin": ["Portsmouth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "102"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "76"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r652706479-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["If having regular afternoon tea the only issues would be ambience (Tv on instead of relaxing music) and service (had to refill our own hot water pot amongst other issues).", "Also neither of us drink alcohol but we weren't offered an alternative. ", "However, if you have ANY dietary requirements please avoid. I had contacted the hotel by email and messenger to ensure my afternoon tea was a) gluten free and b) free of salmon and mustard and b) that my partner had no pork.", "Rang bell ignored - staff on mobiles taking pictures", "Tapped on door let in but not warm welcome", "Given gluten free sandwiches for me and gluten free cakes and scones for both of us. Had long wait for partners sandwiches. I said that my partner wasnt gluten free so would want normal cakes and scones. ", "15 minutes later after i had eaten most of the gluten free cakes I was informed they weren't gluten free as advised by the waiter.", "They are lucky it wasn't my daughter with her peanut allergy or theyd be dealing with a dead body.", "Manager was great but it was too late then.", "Disappointing Valentine's day"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r652930863", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Disgusting Food", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "17 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "LondonTravelerr", "reviewer_origin": ["Brighton and Hove, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r652930863-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["The first time we visited the food was outstanding, The 2nd time, The food was really really bad. We had 3 courses and the food was either burnt or undercooked, The food was inedible and we left most of the food, We complained and was given 20% off next visit. What a joke. I won't be going back at all ,"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r665753216", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointing afternoon tea, far better at the Hilton Park Lane.", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "12 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "finkfloydman", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "247"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "428"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r665753216-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["My wife and I have enjoyed a couple of afternoon teas at the Hilton on Park Lane (plus at other establishments) and once again we had a Buyagift voucher. For this afternoon tea, we chose the Cinnamon Restaurant at the Hilton Hotel, Canary Wharf.", "On entering the restaurant, we were shown to our table for two by the front windows, the afternoon tea side of the restaurant was fairly quiet with just a few other tables occupied. ", "Our \u201csparkling cocktails\u201d which I can only describe as pink grapefruit was not quite what we were expecting. My wife had a pot of tea which wasn\u2019t very hot and I had a coffee. Our three-tier tower of sandwiches and mini cakes arrived soon after. The four quarters of sandwich with various fillings were very small and barely made up one decent sandwich and some of the bread was a little on the dry side. The cakes too were a little uninspiring although the warm scones with jam and clotted cream were good.", "At no time were we asked if everything was ok but I did ask the waiter for another coffee. We were never asked if we would like any more but reading other reviews, I get the impression you are charged. At the Hilton Park Lane, they offered us another tier of food without charge and even then, asked us would we like anymore.", "The ambiance of the Cinnamon restaurant wasn\u2019t very inspiring with drab brown d\u00e9cor. The outlook from the windows looks across a busy main road with a building site opposite plus you have the rumbling of the DLR trains almost above your head. ", "All-in-all a rather disappointing experience and not a patch on the Park Lane Hilton."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r656083760", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Restaurant visit", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "3 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "NayoLights", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r656083760-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited the hotel for my husbands birthday, we used a Wowcher code for the restaurant. Unfortunately staff was so concerned about expressing and placing emphasis on the voucher code. I explained that money was not an issue, which I feel that we should not have had to explain. I requested for a slice of cake to be brought out as a surprise and explained I was happy to again PAY EXTRA. They totally ignored the request and brought out cold food. The food was nice, but it can out in the wrong order. ", "In addition they added a service charge, which I explained I was not happy to pay as our steaks where bloody and had to be sent back. ", "Our sides were delivered cold and no cake was brought even though I had requested it. ", "We was forced to pay the service charge to avoid and arguement. ", "Service was incredibly lousy"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r660825292", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Wowcher Roast Dinner with bottle of wine for 2", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "24 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Trevor S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "63"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r660825292-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["I wasn't overly concerned when I saw quite a few bad reviews as I prefer to judge for myself. I visited with my wife on Sat 23rd March for the roasting board dinner with bottle of wine for 2. We were greeted on arrival to the restaurant by a gentleman who was quite pleasant and we were seated. The restaurant was pretty empty at the time and we were given the option of a bottle of red or white wine and a choice of either meat, fish or veggie. We opted for the meat which consisted of steak, chicken, potatoes and vegetables. It took about 20 minutes to arrive but was served very hot and I found the meal very tasty. There was more than enough for the 2 of us. We paid \u00a329 instead of \u00a375. At \u00a329 I think this was very reasonable but wouldn't want to pay the full \u00a375. Our experience was very good and I would recommend to others if this wowcher is still available. No service charge was added but we tipped the waiter a fiver anyway. I've eaten at many different restaurants and have had worse experiences at other so called 5 star ones."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r634048481", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "A uge disappointment", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "17 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "poweecutee", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r634048481-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Having the knowledge that it is a lovely restaurant, and not to mention in Hilton, my expectation is high. ", "When we came, to my surprise, we were directed and sat at the Bar area. The Supervisor (Asian/Indian) saw the look on my face, he immediately stated, \u201cRoasting Board is on that side\u201d. Almost like, you have a Wowcher voucher so you are not sitting at the restaurant. ", "Take note, our booking stated Seating Area is at the Cinnamon Restaurant \u201cNot Bar!\u201d", "After our order was taken, we waited for over 30mins for our food to come. ", "When the waitress served the roasting board, she dropped the pepper shaker and it smashed on the floor. She apologised but there was no sense of urgency to clear it up. So I went to the bar and called the waitress and asked to clear it. ", "The waitress then came over with an aggressive attitude to clear the broken ceramics, with no intention to check if it is all clear and safe. Therefore, I had to call her back as there is another big piece of the broken ceramic just beside my friends chair. ", "When she came to bring the plates, she just shove it on our table with no care whatsoever. ", "On top of this disgraceful customer service, the waitress has a very bad body odour. ", "It is such a pity that we had a truly unpleasant experience because the food is actually really nice. ", "However, I will never recommend this restaurant at all nor will return. ", "Thought the whole idea is to be able to introduce the restaurant to new clients and have a great experience, but this was not the case on this occasion sadly."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r619764486", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Delicious afternoon tea", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "26 September 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "pjk7", "reviewer_origin": ["Ware, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "147"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "48"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r619764486-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We enjoyed our afternoon tea, the sandwiches, cakes and scones were all fresh and the service was very good. We ordered an extra pot of tea each with no charge. The pannacotta was delicious. The only reason I didn't give 5 stars was because it would have been much nicer to be on a higher level and not the ground level where the view was a road with a railway line going above it. I have been in a few Hiltons where the restaurant/bar area is on an upper floor."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r617907488", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Afternoon tea without tea", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "19 September 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SprogLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "195"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "77"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r617907488-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["This must rate as the worst afternoon tea we have ever experienced. The restaurant is without any sort of atmosphere not helped by the fact there was only one other couple when we went.", "The \u201ccocktail\u201d was more like a sugar syrup so it didn\u2019t start well and went down hill from there. The cakes and sandwiches arrived on such a tall stand that when it was placed in the middle of the table we couldn\u2019t see each other and no tea. After a time the waitress appeared and my husband asked where the tea was. She returned shortly with a pot and we asked if there was a choice and she said there was but we were not offered any so stayed with the breakfast tea she has bought.", "Both sandwiches and cakes were very cheap looking tasteless bread and unexceptional fillings. Cheap jam with the scones which were the most edible part of the tea.", "Save your money and go to Pret so much nicer and tastier."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r621113588", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Sunday Lunch ", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "1 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Agbaman", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "112"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r621113588-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for Sunday lunch on a Wowcher voucher and must say I was very impressed by the overall experience. Staff where very nice the ambiance was also relaxing. The selection of food was also very ok. Downside is there is no parking but location is close to the train station "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r620896995", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Whata breakfast", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "1 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "daveturnkey", "reviewer_origin": ["Sandbach, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r620896995-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Used this resturant during a stay at the Hilton for breakfast only. There is a great choice and the staff are really quick to get you drinks and clear plates etc. Excellent place to eat."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r623176044", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great breakfast", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "8 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SARAH C", "reviewer_origin": ["Maidstone, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r623176044-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We stayed in the hotel and had breakfast included. Huge selection of cooked and continental. Even a pancake station. Good quality food, well cooked and fresh. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r623954532", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Afternoon tea in the Cinnamon Restaurant", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "11 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Nigel R", "reviewer_origin": ["Leicester, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "119"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r623954532-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We used a buyagift voucher for a sparkling afternoon tea in the Cinnamon Restaurant. The staff were friendly and welcoming. The sparking cocktail and food was very good. My only criticism is that the restaurant is rather characterless and being on the ground floor, had no views worth mentioning."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r615409673", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Minimalism is not good for an afternoon tea.", "diner_date": " September 2018", "rating_date": "10 September 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Martin Y,", "I appreciate your review of your recent experience at our Cinnamon Restaurant and Bar. I'm very sorry you had a disappointing experience with us, and I addressed these issues with our staff for the lack of communication in regarding the second serve of tea, coffees and scones. ", "Nevertheless I would like to state that we charge \u00a34,50 for extra plates of sandwiches or cakes if you are using one of our third party promotions. Yet a la carte guest have one second serve of sandwiches or cakes included.", "Exceptional guest service is the foundation of our brand promise. Your feedback helps us improve. Thank you once again for your comments.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MASH000001", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "179"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "58"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r615409673-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We had four quarters of a sandwich, each with a different filling, which means the total of one full sandwich. We had one scone each, we had four cakes, as in a muffin, a brownie and two other things and that was it. One pot of teah each which consisted of two cups. Never offered any more sandwiches, cakes or scones and never offered any more tea, infact, not once did anybody come to us and asked if everything was ok. Ate the sandwiches, the scone and two of the cakes and left."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r624898990", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Pleasant experience ", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "15 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "skaurs", "reviewer_origin": ["Hornchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r624898990-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a wowcher for roasting board which included a bottle of wine, the food was lovely a good selection and enough for 2 people! Staff were friendly and the place overall was nice and clean! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r627427947", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very poor", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "23 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kendoherty70", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "117"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "35"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r627427947-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a table booked for 9, took the waiter ages to come and take our order - we ordered from the set menu, the drinks arrived fairly quickly but no food whatsoever was received until nearly half ten (and when food did arrive, the starter was probably the smallest starter I\u2019ve ever had in a restaurant, I\u2019ve been served bigger amuse-bouches for free elsewhere) The mains didn\u2019t arrive until ten to eleven and the chicken breast was like a bog-standard Hunters Chicken that you can find on most pubs menu (and a pub cook would probably pay more care and attention to make it look more appealing than what arrived at our table) Dessert finally arrived at quarter past eleven, a chocolate fondant that was ok but wouldn\u2019t win any awards. The waiter continually kept on about how busy they were on a Monday night, but I would have said there were only 20 or so other people in the restaurant at the same time as us: the couple one side ordered steaks, but they must have waited the best part of an hour for the side vegetables to arrive, and the lady of the couple said her steak was seriously over cooked (although their steaks must have been stone cold by the time the vegetables arrived), and the couple the other side had plates with their leftovers piled up for a good two hours or so before anyone bothered to clear their table. We were offered free coffees as an apology for the time it took to get our food, alas they were nondescript cups of semi-warm, milky water so we left sharpish at this point. It was about twenty to twelve when we finally left - hard to imagine how it could take anyone so long to serve up what was essentially not a lot of food."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r612331410", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Shocking experience - DO NOT RECOMMEND", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "30 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Ipdoris4,", "Thank you very much for your constructive feedback and I was disappointed to hear that our service were not satisfactory to you.", " ", "I also would like to apologize for the the kids behavior on that night. Our Restaurant and Bar normally welcome family groups specially those staying in the Hotel, and during summer holidays the numbers of family groups rises significantly. ", "Nevertheless I would like to respectfully highlight that as far as I could understand about the events of that night my team did their part by asking the parents to keep their kids under control, please note that we can not interfere on families parenting style.", "We appreciate the comments and we hope to be able to welcome you back sometime in the future.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Dori_pingu", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r612331410-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["A shocking experience dining at Cinnamon on Thursday evening 23 August with my boyfriend. There was one female server who was friendly and polite but frankly lost control of the restaurant. At the time there were only two families at the very back of the dining area and they just let their kids go wild - they were screaming, running up and down the hallway of the restaurant, pushing and throwing toy cars everywhere, and chasing each other around in groups of 3-4.... It was nothing you'd expect from dining in a hotel and the waitress did not even try and do something about it.", "Moreover, the waitress was also slow and took forever to take our order - we were honestly so close to leaving. The food itself was OK, made up for the awful atmosphere, screaming noise and environment in which we were eating. We would definitely NOT return back and do NOT recommend this restaurant to anyone. Having lived in London for 8+ years now, it was the worst dining experience in a mid-range restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r584120733", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Cant complain", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "31 May 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Sjclarke1978,", "Firstly thank you for your feedback.", "I am happy to read your compliments of our service, menu options. We appreciate your recommendation and look forward to welcoming you back again.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sjclarke1978", "reviewer_origin": ["Derby, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "104"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r584120733-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Service was good, very respectful. Small choice of beers, menu had good options and the food was pretty good for a hotel restaurant. I would definitely return if staying in the hotel."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r588870631", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "groupon Burger and Pint deal", "diner_date": " June 2018", "rating_date": "19 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear NED180,", "Thank you for your feedback which certainly helps us to monitor and improve our services. ", "I am pleased that overall you had a nice experience and found our team to be friendly. Once again, Thank you for your time to review us. Myself and my team we hope to have the opportunity of welcoming you back again.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "NED180", "reviewer_origin": ["Halifax, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "94"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r588870631-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["found this deal on groupon for 2 burgers and 2 pints and as we would be in the area and it was our anniversary we decided to give it a go as its a little bit special ", "we made the booking for 3pm and when arrived we were told the booking was for the bar not the restaurant which we didn't mind but we were the only ones in the bar at that time so no atmosphere. the very nice waiter came and took our order, we ordered the chefs burger and the lamb burger with 2 pints of Becks. The burger thick and tasty the chips were ok but I think I may have been expecting a little more from the Hilton so upto this point I was marking it a 3 star but the extra star goes for them bringing out a beautiful slate of chocolate cake to celebrate our wedding anniversary so thank you very much this was very nice and the cake very very nice."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r583922638", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Tea Afternoon", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "30 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MyrtleM_13", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r583922638-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["A huge disappointment.", "The sandwiches were micro with hardly any filling,the cakes not spectacular and the scones were dry !", "The Earl Grey tea was a teabag !!!!!! I could not believe that a Hilton hotel would serve teabags instead of tea leaves that give more flavour.", "The only good thing was the cocktail. ", "The staff were pleasant!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r589591807", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "afternoon tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "21 June 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Queentea2016,", "Thank you for your feedback which certainly helps us to monitor and improve our services. I'm sorry that you were not directed straight after your arrival to our Executive Lounge as per your third party promotion. Nevertheless we are glad that you found our afternoon tea to be pleasant.", "I note your comments that you haven't been served an non-alcoholic drink instead of our normal Sparkling Cocktail. Yet I would like to state that we do exchange the standard drink for soft drinks upon guest request.", "Once again, thank you for your valuable feedback and hope to have the opportunity of welcoming you back again.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "queentea2016", "reviewer_origin": ["Greater London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r589591807-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["I went here for the afternoon tea purchased through wowcher", "We were initially told to sit on the ground floor with the view of a building site to look at, even though the voucher specifies a higher floor.", "We did get taken upstairs after raising this and the remainder of the afternoon tea was pleasant, although we didn\u2019t get a choice of mocktail to drink in place of the free cocktail."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r594992504", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious breakfast", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "10 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Herbys123,", "Firstly thank you for your feedback.", "Our Restaurant Team thrives to go above and beyond each day to ensure that our guests receive the service deserved. I am pleased to read that you enjoyed our service and food. Thank you for the high scores and your time. ", "I hope that myself and my team will have the opportunity to welcome you and your family back to our Restaurant in a near future.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Herbys123", "reviewer_origin": ["Cannock, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "56"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r594992504-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Plenty of choice, nobody goes hungry here. Good selection of fruit & cold buffet breakfast then the Hot selection, chef on hand to personally cook omelette with lots of fillings, boiled eggs, fried eggs Scrambled eggs. Waffles with syrup. Porridge & cereals. ", "Teas & Coffee. Juices & chilled water. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r599798750", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Family Dining at Cinnamon", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "26 July 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Wratwood,", "Thank you for taking your time to give your feedback. ", "I was delighted to read that you and your family had a good experience. Thank you for your kind comments and high scores. I hope that myself and my team will have the pleasure of welcoming you and your family back to our Restaurant.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "wratwood", "reviewer_origin": ["Chicago, Illinois"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "40"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r599798750-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We are staying eight nights at the Hilton Canary Wharf. We have had dinner twice from Cinnamon. My son\u2019s steak was surprisingly good; by burger was OK; salads were good; I think our favorite was the Chicken Tika Masala. Breakfast buffet is included with our room and is very good and varied."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r607269099", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent service, great food", "diner_date": " July 2018", "rating_date": "17 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Jolien K,", "Thank you for choosing the Cinnamon Restaurant and Bar. I was delighted to read that you had a good experience and that you enjoyed your visit. Thank you for your high scores and kind comments, especially with regards to the team. I shall ensure that your kind words are passed on to the team.", "We appreciate your feedback and look forward to welcoming you back soon.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jolien K", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r607269099-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Great choice if you're looking for a restaurant in the Canary Wharf and London area, it's worth a bit of travel as service is excellent.", "Came with the family and got the family offer, great value for money. Kids enjoyed the meals form the kids menu and we had the steak with chips. Yummy!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r609954863", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Poor service and bad food", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "24 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Vonvintlo,", "Thank you for your review and apologies for not pleasing you on all counts. We appreciate the comments and hope to have the opportunity of welcoming you back to our Restaurant again.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "VonVintlo", "reviewer_origin": ["Johannesburg, South Africa"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "155"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r609954863-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Very understaffed at dinner, food is poor, you are better going out to the mall for dinner. Breakfast wasnt any better"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r611466956", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "More than Expected", "diner_date": " August 2018", "rating_date": "28 August 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear OverTheRainbowLondon,", "We are glad to read your positive review!", "We apologise for the issue with the speed of our services: please rest assured that your comment have been discussed with our team, in order to improve things for the future.", "We sincerely hope to welcome you back soon!", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "OverTheRainbowLondon", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r611466956-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Service was a little slow but polite and friendly. The hotel is close to Canary Wharf station and not far from the London Docklands Museum which is excellent. We had a Wowcher deal for a roasting board and wine and were pleasantly surprised at the quality and quantity of the serving. We had contemplated getting additional sides but the board had greens, broccoli, mac and cheese, a steak cooked as we had requested, roasted chicken breasts, roasted vegetables, 'ju', horseradish, Yorkshire puddings and even a couple of onion rings so definitely enough for us both. We also ordered a cheese board which is enough for two and were able to swap the bottle of wine to a large glass and a tea and non-alcoholic drink. I'm not sure I'd pay the full price (\u00a375) unless they get something we didn't but we felt very good value on the voucher and only paid a service charge on the additional items."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r583675153", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect for city trips, awesome breakfast", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "29 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mitudd1979", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r583675153-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We did a London Trip with our son. Hilton Hotel was perfect for trips to downtown. Staff and breakfast were perfect. Our waiter Constantin Cenusa was one of the best we've ever had.", "Wonderfull days in a wonderfull Hotel!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r566088686", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average...", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "12 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "kuczikd", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "16"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r566088686-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited before couple of times and was always happy with the service, but on this occasion you failed to deliver... quality of food (had better) is not something the staff can affect, but being difficult at the welcome desk is definitely something they could. We have reserved a table through a 3rd party and were faulted for not calling the hotel, restaurant was empty but rather than just seating us, the girl started arguing and tried to educate us. As I have worked many years in hospitality, i know that customer is always number one, unfortunately not for the staff at Hilton Canary Wharf..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r567033334", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Disastrous afternoon tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "17 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Thunderchild85", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r567033334-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We attended on a quiet Friday for afternoon tea. To begin with they couldn't find our reservation. We were seated quickly then forgotten about. Other customers were being seated and given drinks.", "After 30 minutes of enduring thirst we managed to flag someone down to ask for a drinks menu. After all, what's an afternoon tea without tea?! The food arrived shortly afterwards which tasted quite stale and shop bought. A glass of cheap Prosecco in the form of an apology from the manager, was not good enough.", "I overheard the the extremely unprofessional staff complaining that they were overbooked and wouldn't be able accommodate all the bookings if they turned up on time. I have no experience in the hospitality industry but surely it would have made sense to get us in, fed and quickly out? Instead we were ignored for over half an hour without any acknowledgement from staff and left without anything to drink or eat. To summarise: unprofessional management, poor food and terrible service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r564974490", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Afternoon tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "6 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "HolidayCG G", "reviewer_origin": ["St Albans, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "9"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r564974490-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Booked afternoon tea for my wife\u2019s birthday. Monday afternoon so restaurant was expectedly quiet, fine by me. Food was ok, standard set-up, cakes a bit dry. Good choice of tea.", "Considering it was quiet and they had a lot of staff present it was not nice to see 3 tables around us that hadn\u2019t been cleared when we first got there, 30 minutes before they were done.", "We also waited a long time to get the food.", "They did however redeem themselves somewhat by laying on a \u2018happy birthday\u2019 plate with fruit and chocolate cake, many thanks for that!", "During the meal, we would have loved it if a member of staff would have asked if everything was ok, would have really appreciated another pot of tea with those dry cakes!!", "In summary, we shopped around and paid \u00a320 for afternoon tea for two, what we got was decent value for money but the service needs to improve a bit. 7/10"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r568678669", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely sparkling afternoon tea", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "25 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kerry H", "reviewer_origin": ["Billericay, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r568678669-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited on a Sunday with a booking for 1pm using a Buy a Gift voucher. We were seated quickly & a glass of prosecco with strawberry pur\u00e9e was brought up straight away. The restaurant wasn't busy and diners were spread out rather than being put in one area which was nice as didn't feel cramped. The cream tea selection was good with four different sandwiches, a fruit scone & a selection of cakes. Neither myself or my daughter like tea or coffee but we were happily offered alternatives at no extra cost. Service was good & friendly & we were asked more than once if everything was ok. Overall a lovely, relaxed cream tea"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r569866927", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Skylounge Afternoon Tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "31 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KerryMarie87", "reviewer_origin": ["Kingston upon Thames, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "28"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "43"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r569866927-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["My friend and I went here as a gift for my 30th on a buyagift deal that she kindly got for me. We had both been to a few really great afternoon tea places before, being a Hilton we had high expectations for this one. Sadly it was rather disappointing...aesthetically it looked great, and the views were good; however it took almost an hour after we were served our tea for the food to arrive, when it did arrive the sandwiches were quite soggy, rather bland, and the scones tasted a little on the stale side, the tiffin mini dessert was so horrid I had to discreetly spit it into my napkin. If you had never experienced afternoon tea before I\u2019m sure this would have been a nice experience, having been to a few other places (most likely for half the price) this was a huge letdown. I was just very pleased to be in great company!", "I would not recommend afternoon tea at the Hilton."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r568579740", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Afternoon tea with family and a wowcher discount ", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "25 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mediterranea3", "reviewer_origin": ["Budapest, Hungary"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "254"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "285"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r568579740-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Afternoon tea with children", "Well it was ok, not luxurious as other Hilton hotel branch though but manager tried her best to accommodate our halal meat diet, which was very kind, ", "in the other hand the portion were small, we asked more (children were hungry and liked the sandwiches) but she had a long explaination how business works (?! unnecessary we not here for that, plus I'm working in silver hospitality for years... My advice is Keep it simple) and because of the wowcher deal, they do charge 4,5\u00a3 for an extra plate which is not bad, ", "The place was nice and quiet for a Saturday afternoon", "Children happy, parents relaxed :)", "Thank you Beatriz"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r572820630", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Food average, waitress very poor service and rude", "diner_date": " April 2018", "rating_date": "12 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "chels_p14", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r572820630-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited on Monday 9 April 2017 for afternoon tea, having been bought a gift voucher from buy a gift.", "On arrival, there were only two members of staff for the restaurant- the restaurant front of house (and assuming supervisor given the different uniform) and a waitress.", "We approached the restaurant desk, and the waitress saw us, but stood staring for 5-10 mins before then asking if we'd like to sit down.", "We didn't have to wait long for our food, but the service was terrible. The supervisor who brought the food over said the waitress would be over to take our tea order, but she wasn't. We had to flag her down, and when politely asking if we could order our teas, the reception we were given was that we were asking for blood. I don't know about you, but i thought one of the key elements of afternoon TEA is tea after all!", "The food was average- nothing special, standard cakes. The scones were lovely and had been warmed through which was a nice touch, but the cakes (brownie and fruitcake) were dry and tasteless.", "I wasn't expecting Michelin star, but was disappointed in the lack of service. I'd approached the waitress to ask where the toilet was, and was greeted with a 'what'. That's fine if you didn't hear me, but basic manners, particularly in hospitality can go a long way. Even after repeating myself, the response was cold and rude- an abrupt 'down the stairs' and walked off.", "Given other reviews i'd read about the service, after our own experience, i'd highly suggest further training on waiting staff on basic manners- or better still, hire staff that actually want to be there.", "The service the restaurant provides brings down the Hilton name.", "We will not be returning again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r573083223", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food, excellent service!", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "13 April 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "VCMO", "reviewer_origin": ["Accra, Ghana"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "128"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "40"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r573083223-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Had dinner three nights in a row. The menu is simple and to the point. The service is excellent even though at times it seems like Rita is the only one on duty but she was superb; very pleasant, excellent attitude and super efficient even with a full house. Had the Rib Eye steak the first night and it was so good I didn't want it to get finished. Thought of having the same thing the next day but opted for the grilled salmon which gave me the same feeling as the Rib Eye; I wished it didn't get finished! On my 3rd night I had the corn fed chicken breast which was ok though not as filling as the grills which is what I'd recommend. ", "The menu is basically in two sections: grills with separate sides or mains inclusive of sides. The grills are really well done though a little pricier coz you have to order separate sides. Prices range between \u00a317-20 for the mains including sides and between \u00a317-26 for the grills excluding the side dishes which average around \u00a34 each. Gets very busy on Friday and Saturday nights so important to make a prior reservation."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r579941267", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Superb breakfast (and staff!)", "diner_date": " May 2018", "rating_date": "13 May 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RoryMorty", "reviewer_origin": ["Giessen, Germany"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "309"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "239"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r579941267-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["I recently stayed at the Hilton London Canary Wharf, and used the Cinnamon Restaurant and Bar, which is located on the ground floor level of the Hotel, for breakfast every day. The restaurant does not disappoint! The staff are extremely friendly, and the breakfast selection is outstanding, in particular, the full English fare, as well as all the hot and cold extra's. The ma\u00eetre d', whose name I missed, is arguable the most friendly and efficient of any I have ever encountered! ", "I look forward to my next indulgence at the Cinnamon Restaurant and Bar, and I am excited to try out one of their afternoon teas, which looked great from a distance as well!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r564581547", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Nice bar.", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "5 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Mr. Anthonyl994,", "Thank you for your visit to our Cinnamon Restaurant and Bar and for giving us such a glowing review!", "I was delighted to see that you enjoyed your time with us and we hope to welcome you back in the very near future!", "Best regards,", "Beatriz Machado"], "reviewer_pseudo": "anthonyl994", "reviewer_origin": ["Sheffield"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r564581547-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Used the bar at the Hilton Canary Wharf 3 times during our stay. Every time was a good experience with professional, helpful and pleasant bar staff. The seating areas were numerous and clean. The surroundings had a spacious and bright feel.", "Would recommend the Cinnamon Bar for a drink and a quality bar snack when you are in the area. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r559140084", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Afternoon tea with Buyagift", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "8 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We appreciate the time taken to post your feedback. I was happy to hear that you had an enjoyable Afternoon Tea and found our services and food to be good.", "My apologies regarding the temperature of hot water provided for your Tea, we already fixed the problem highlighted. Once again Thank you for your visit, we look forward to welcoming you back in the near future.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado - F&B Supervisor"], "reviewer_pseudo": "sallyann46", "reviewer_origin": ["Rochester UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "27"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r559140084-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Enjoyed my birthday treat with my daughter. The service was good & the afternoon tea sandwiches, scones & pastries were delicious. My only issue was with the tea, the tea pots were delivered with \u201chot\u201d water, with a selection of tea bags on the table. We asked for more water, but that also wasn\u2019t hot enough either."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r555181446", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Birthday sparkling afternoon tea", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "21 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Ms. Julie,", "We appreciate the time taken to post your feedback. I was happy to hear that you had an enjoyable Afternoon Tea experience and found the services and food to be good. We look forward to welcoming you back in the near future.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado - F&B Supervisor"], "reviewer_pseudo": "julie g", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r555181446-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["My daughter booked sparkling afternoon tea for the 2 of us.", "We were booked in at reception by a friendly and polite member of staff, who also asked if we had any dietary requirements ( my daughter is allergic to fish) so was pleased we were asked.", "We were offered as much tea to drink as we liked, the selection of tea was very good.", "The sandwiches and cakes were brought over and we were told what the different fillings were. The selection was lovely, nice and fresh and plenty for us, we were full up.", "We were then brought a bottle of prosecco, which was a big surprise as we were only expecting a glass each. We were offered more tea or asked if we would like coffee.", "The staff were very friendly and attentive and we are looking forward to going back"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r555473883", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Terrible food and poor service", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "22 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "We regret that we were not able to provide you with the quality of service you deserve during your recent visit. We strive for unparalleled service delivery at our hotel, and we are always looking for ways to ensure that each guest experiences the very best we have to offer. We believe that very best service experiences are genuine, anticipatory and personalized and we will continue to work to ensure our guests find that level of service at our hotel. Your feedback will help us to continue to improve our training processes, and we hope you will return to visit us to experience the results of that work first-hand. ", "Kind Regards,", "Beatriz Machado - F&B Supervisor"], "reviewer_pseudo": "MattN1971", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "30"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r555473883-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["I went her for lunch with a couple of colleagues. We ordered our food from the barman, who came to our table without a pen or paper, so we should have known he might get one of the orders wrong, but he successfully managed to get all 3 wrong!!! Might be an idea to invest in a pen and paper instead of trying to be too clever. My steak when it arrived was disgusting. I could tell it had been cooked straight from frozen and was tough and chewy, which would indicate it had probably been in the freezer for a few months. The salmon arrived and was black it was so overcooked and was extremely dry. Even when the manageress came over to try and rectify the situation, she got our order wrong!!! As I was leaving the manageress did tr and make amends by inviting me back for a complimentary meal and giving me her business card. The fact I have declined to eat there for free should tell everyone all they need t know about the restaurant at Hilton Docklands. It's a real shame as Cinnamon used to be quite good and I would eat there a couple of times a week, but the quality of food and standard of service are dreadful. Without a doubt, the food quality is no better than 2 star, regardless of what star the hotel is. In future if I want a steak I will pop to Goodmans, which is 2 minute walk from the hotel and 200 times better than the Hilton's poor efforts. Just not good enough from a supposed good brand, what has happened to Hilton?!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r559659754", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointing afternoon tea at Cinnamon", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "10 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Kikirae86,", "Thank you very much for your constructive feedback and apologies for not pleasing you and your partner. In behalf of my team I am disappointed to hear that our standards of service were not satisfactory to you.", "We appreciate the comments and we hope to be able to welcome you back sometime in the future."], "reviewer_pseudo": "kikirae86", "reviewer_origin": ["Whiteley, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "24"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r559659754-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["My husband and I purchased a Groupon voucher for afternoon tea at Cinnamon restaurant for our wedding anniversary.", "We arrived early and had expected to have to wait but were shown straight to our table. Our sparkling cocktails came out straight away, as did the tea/coffee order and our afternoon tea plate. At no point were we asked about allergies etc. and we had made the reservation through the Groupon link so there was no opportunity to say. ", "The cakes served were dry and far from fresh, especially the red velvet ones. My husband and I highlighted this and were given new 'fresh' cakes, which were very cold and appeared to have been excessively chilled or frozen."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r562725524", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Bad Afternoon tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "25 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Ms, Viktorria F,", "First of all, thank you for your review.", "I apologize that we were unable to immediately accommodate you to your reserved table. We also regret that we were not able to provide you with the quality of service you deserve. Your feedback will help us to continue to improve our training processes, and we hope you will return to visit our restaurant to experience the results of that work first-hand.", "Once again, thank you for bringing this to my attention and I hope that we will have an opportunity to welcome you back. Please feel free to contact me directly to make your reservation in the future."], "reviewer_pseudo": "Vyxykee", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "53"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r562725524-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["we bought on groupon an afternoon tea. I made the reservation via groupon. When we arrived they couldn\u2019t find my reservation. After 10 minutes arguing my partner asked them that they have a table or not for us. They said yes they have but next time make sure we book the reservation directly with them. We sat down and they straight bring the glass of bubbly what it was include our deal. They didnt even asked are we want now or later. The food was absolutely not the hilton standard. The teas are nothing special. They have twining tea branch what i could by in tesco as well. Be honest i would expect much more for hilton. It was very bad quality food and service."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r560220921", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Ruined my special occasion", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "13 February 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Srushti P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r560220921-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["I had purchased one of the 'popular' packages with Wowcher for Valentines Day. The fine print or Terms stated nothing about exceptions to special days and occasions as is usually provided by most restaurants. Wowcher TnCs require them to provide the services subject to the fine print. However the manager refused to honour the voucher even though he acknowledged that it was no fault of mine. ", "Honestly, it made me feel like the package was free to begin with and he was doing me a favour, rather than a promotional pre-purchase deal.", "Despite promising to get back to me and a follow up mail from Wowcher themselves, the Manager just didn't bother to get back to us. ", "Having a chance to go through the other reviews, I realise that I'm not the only one who has had a bad experience re:bookings. ", "Needless to say, I would never recommend this place to anyone."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r563116911", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Afternoon tea", "diner_date": " February 2018", "rating_date": "27 February 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Susan,", "First of all, thank you for your review of your recent visit at our Cinnamon Restaurant.", "I apologize that we were unable to provide a takeaway box for your cakes, as I also apologize to read that some charges were applied for a second plate of sandwiches. This has now been changed, because above all our Guests feedback is incredibly important to us. Our Restaurant team thrives to go above and beyond each day to ensure that our guests receive the service deserved.", "Once again, thank you for your review."], "reviewer_pseudo": "susancraven2017", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "6"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r563116911-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["The worse afternoon tea I have had, we were charged extra money as we requested ", "More sandwiches I don\u2019t think one round of sandwiches per people is enough, there was more waiting staff that guests no back ground music just a large TV on the wall", "Showing BBC news", " we requested a take away box to take home the cakes which had not been eaten was told they did not allow this which I was very angry with as before at other hotels", "they always offered a take away box ", "my advice save you money and go else where"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r564308115", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food with several gluten free options", "diner_date": " March 2018", "rating_date": "4 March 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear 136HelenB,", "Thank you for choosing the Cinnamon Restaurant and Bar. I was delighted to read that you had a good experience and that you enjoyed your our food and service. Thank you for your kind comments and high scores. I hope that we have the pleasure of welcoming you back soon.", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado."], "reviewer_pseudo": "136HelenB", "reviewer_origin": ["Shefford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r564308115-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Cinnamon Restaurant had several dishes on their evening menu which were gluten free- very helpful staff who were happy to go and check with the chef. No GF desserts available though.", "Breakfast- not only did they have gluten free bread available, but also a separate toaster! Somewhat a miracle in hotels- some either dont have gluten free bread or think its ok to put GF bread on their normal toaster. Buffet breakfast, good options for hot and cold."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r563842409", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Afternoon Tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "3 March 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "scotth226", "reviewer_origin": ["Hastings, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "48"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r563842409-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["My expectations were high and looking forward to a luxury experience. It all went down hill as soon as we arrived. A maintenance man was standing the bar fixing a light fixture the whole duration we there. The restaurant was cold and lacked atmosphere and when i asked if the heating could be tuned up the head waiter just grunted at me. The sandwiches lacked any substance and were poor quality salmon and cream cheese, cucumber and cream cheese and ham and mustard two quarters of each variety per couple. If you do the maths you realise you don\u2019t even get a whole sandwich per person. NOW the tea one TEA BAG per person, yes I said a tea bag. The service i am not even going there."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r554375269", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Afternoon tea with buyagift", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "17 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Guest,", "Thank you for your feedback which certainly helps us to monitor and improve our services. We regret that you did not find the service up to your expectations. ", "Please accept our apologies for the shortfall in service standards you received.", "Once again we thank you for taking your time to provide us with such valuable feedback. This will help us to continue to improve our training processes, and we hope you will return to visit us to experience the results of that work first-hand. ", "Warm Regards,", "Beatriz Machado - F&B Supervisor"], "reviewer_pseudo": "807yend", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r554375269-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We arrived a little early and were ignored by a barman until my friend asked him whether we could be seated. We were then approached by Leo who asked if I brought my buyagift voucher. I told him I wasn't aware I had to as I assumed it was all confirmed electronically. He seated us anyway then said it will be \u00a323 per person. I said no, I'd rather cancel if that's the case. He confirmed our dietary requirements then left us. About 10mins later, he came back with our mocktails and wanting to clarify the situation, I asked will we be charged? He then said I might be able to provide voucher details via email and they'd do all the chasing up. Confused, we nevertheless had our drinks and he returned almost immediately with our tower of sandwiches and treats (which makes me feel it wasn't freshly prepared). We had 4 small triangles of sandwiches each (so barely a full sandwich which is pretty stingy) and the cakes were on par with supermarket long life cakes (dry and uninspiring). The warm scones were the only real treat. For \u00a323 a head, I'd feel very short changed.", "Overall, I think not having the voucher to hand put everything on the wrong foot but the experience even with a voucher is severely lacking. I booked here after reading the good reviews and was disappointed to say the least."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r537393635", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Very poor service", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "31 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mcullen2015", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r537393635-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a Wowcher deal, steak board and a bottle of wine for two, we were greeted by our name which was on a list and shown to a table in the hotel restaurant which apart from us and one other couple was empty. we were asked would we like to have our cocktail first which confused us as we were having a bottle of wine with our deal. we voiced this to the chap who had shown us to our table. he went away to check our booking and said we had to leave the restaurant and escorted us to the hotel bar area which looked like it needed some tables cleaned and said we had to eat there.he then gave us our menus and said the guy behind the bar would come and take our order which he eventually did after we called him over. He knew very little about the menu he didn't seem interested in us or the bar which he was in charge of he looked like he was bored and it came across as rude and unprofessional. We had our meal which was stone cold and left. We wont be visiting again anytime soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r544855956", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely dinner ", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "3 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Mr Deeboy,", "Firstly we would like to thank you for your kind review.", "We are glad you enjoyed your evening in our Cinnamon Restaurant, and are of course ", "looking forward seeing you again very soon! :)", "Warm regards,", "Robbert V"], "reviewer_pseudo": "deeboy", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "501"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "494"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r544855956-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We dined here on a Wowcher deal and it was excellent value for money for three courses and a bottle of prosecco to share.", "I'm not a big fan of hotel restaurants. But this one is relaxed and unstuffy, and we liked the modern design.", "Service was warm and attentive and we liked the menu. Eating gluten free was no problem, and my main course steak was cooked to perfection. We enjoyed all of our dishes and would return. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r539588184", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Maitre d' is obvious to his clients", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "9 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ColetteEP", "reviewer_origin": ["Castricum, The Netherlands"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r539588184-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Had breakfast there for four days, every day same thing, you had to wait, he'll be walking around or looking on his list... They really should lose these guys, standing 2 thick and still they cannot cope...Cheese is always out for some reason and a poor choice which is weird because the breakfast choice is quite opulent! Pls ask the Romanian guy for anything and he will help you instantly. Having that guy there improved service no end! "]}
