{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r547230819", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Good food great service", "diner_date": " December 2017", "rating_date": "14 December 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Jenny186338,", "Firstly we would like to thank you for your review.", "We are very pleased to hear that unless there was a misunderstanding, our staff went the extra mile to ", "ensure a great experience. We would love to welcome you back soon at our Cinnamon Restaurant", "Warm regards,", "Robbert V"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Jenny186338", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "32"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r547230819-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["After a misunderstanding with booking restaurant Uppal wanted to ensure we had a great evening and were looked after. We were looked after by Abhishak and I can't praise him enough the food was great and service was impeccable definitely recommend eating here. Only thing is that hotel was very quiet so if you want good good, service and relaxed evening you should try Cinnamon. Thanks for a great evening."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r547285461", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Office party.", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "15 December 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "890happyshopper", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "112"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "26"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r547285461-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Decidedly mediocre. Very warm venue with lack of understanding that multiple bodies don't need heating but air con instead. Food okay but needs a bit of pizzaz. Only thing you seem to be paying for is the location..."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r543607748", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great breakfast service", "diner_date": " November 2017", "rating_date": "27 November 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "flyingcrazycows", "reviewer_origin": ["Kent, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "161"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "48"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r543607748-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Pre ordered breakfast when we booked the hotel. Attentive staff and well layed out help yourself style. Seated easily and fast. good selection of fresh food and you can choose to have a fry up, fresh fruit, pastries, toast, cereals. Lovely."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r550943501", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Worst afternoon Tea ever ! ", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "2 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear Ruby T,", "Please let us first offer you our sincere and profuse apologies for the inconvenience you have experienced, as a result of the handling of your Afternoon Tea at our Cinnamon restaurant.", "We have already been in contact with you personally, and are therefor hoping you are ", "satisfied the way we resolved this matter.", "If you may decide to return back to us in the future, please give us a call and speak with either our Restaurant & Bar Manager or Supervisor on duty.", "Warm regards,", "Robbert V"], "reviewer_pseudo": "Ruby T", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "9"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r550943501-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["The worst afternoon tea experience I have ever had. A catalogue of unprofessional an unrefined behaviour:", "- As we were seated I was asked to pay for the afternoon tea up front. What type of establishment asks you to pay before you have even eaten or drunk a thing? ", "- I had to swiftly make the payment ahead of our special guests arriving ", "- When the food arrived there was no explanation of what was included on the platter ", "- 4 tiny triangles of sandwiches were presented per person, ie 2 slices of bread! Hardly enough for a child! ", "- Cakes were stale, not very tasty, with a limited selection, different to the advertised menu ", "- Scones were limited to one per person ! ", "- The Scones were stale and had been cut in half and reheated, so were hard and cold ", "- Non of the food was replenished as with a standard afternoon tea", "- Tea cups were removed from the table without asking, whilst people were still drinking. We then we had to wait another 15 minutes for the cups to be replaced ", "- 15 minutes later the hot water arrived despite us asking multiple times ", "- Empty milk jugs were placed on the table. Again we had to request this numerous times before a man from the kitchen arrived with a 2litre milk carton to fill up the jugs at our table, how is that acceptable? ", "- The champagne was mixture of strawberry juice and champagne. 70% fruit juice! A straight glass of champagne was not permitted.", "- We were not asked if we wanted anything, we had to get up and look for a member of staff each time we wanted milk, water or additional drinks ", "Despite raising our concerns with the management we were told this was the standard level of service that the Hilton provide. All our concerns were dismissed perhaps this is why payment was requested up front. Most of our time was spent waiting for either hot water or milk, so we couldn\u2019t even enjoy a cup of tea! ", "To add insult to injury the restaurant was empty and yet the service was exceptionally dire . Staff made little effort to ensure a very basic level of service. ", "We booked this venue because we expected a certain level of quality from an established and renowned name such as the Hilton. We were celebrating a special occasion (a baby shower), so booked what we thought what be a trusted name. The whole event was ruined because of the exceptionally poor service. This has left me with a very sour opinion of the Hilton and makes me question its status as a top end hotel! The poor experience has left all 11 of us very disappointed. I welcome the Hilton to comment on how this level of service is acceptable?"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r551546542", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Meal", "diner_date": " January 2018", "rating_date": "4 January 2018", "answer_text": ["Dear richardlangley2016,", "Thank you very much for your kind review.", "We are very pleased to hear you enjoyed your stay at us, and that our staff ensured ", "an outstanding experience for you. Also, we are happy to see you your enthusiasm spreading", "the word!", "We are looking forward welcoming you again anytime soon at the hotel.", "Warm regards,", "Robbert V"], "reviewer_pseudo": "richardlangley2016", "reviewer_origin": ["Ashford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r551546542-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We recently stayed at the Hilton Hotel Canary Wharf and had dinner the first night in the Cinnamon Restaurant. Excellent meal, superb quality with very friendly and attentive staff. Would thoroughly recomend it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r534377534", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Lunch in the middle of office land", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "19 October 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Pauline H", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "39"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "48"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r534377534-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We had lunch on a Groupon voucher. If we only knew what was included in the meal. We ordered far too much as most of it was included in the voucher. Very good value for money. Ambience was typical travellers hotel bar/restaurant not a lot of character. Main meal came before we had finished our starter. Food was tasty and well cooked."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r523082139", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Treated appallingly", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "10 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "harrietsalmons", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r523082139-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Myself and two friends came here for afternoon tea to celebrate my friends 21st birthday and the fact that she had had her last chemotherapy session a few days earlier. On arrival the staff asked us which price we had been quoted as we booked through a secondary website. We were quoted \u00a323 each for afternoon tea including a champagne cocktail and the server charged us as normal.", "We were taken up to the Executive Lounge (which has amazing views) to be given our afternoon tea, however the server then refused to give us champagne as she thought we were underage. We all had ID with us which we showed her, but she then said 'it's not complimentary' so we had to go without.", "This definitely ruined the entire trip as I do not believe we would have been treated as such were we older. I feel like the servers took advantage of us due to our age, and refusing to serve us even after showing IDs is appalling.", "I have since emailed both the restaurant and the hotel itself to complain about this treatment but have received no response.", "I am very disappointed with the overall service and would not recommend it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r493841104", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Afternoon Tea......meh!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "17 June 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "cvwilsonuk", "reviewer_origin": ["Chertsey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "17"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r493841104-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited the hotel as we had an afternoon tea voucher. After booking several months ago and then calling twice in the week leading up to the visit (once to confirm and once to change the time), we were told that they didn't have a reservation for us!! Luckily, the restaurant was empty so they agreed to accommodate us. ", "The place itself is clean but the overall experience was nothing special. The cocktails were brought out pretty much as soon as we sat down but we had to ask for our tea mid way through as no one actually thought to bring us any! ", "Sandwiches were ok but nothing imaginative. 1 raisin scone per person which was nice and quite fresh. Selection of cakes were nice enough but again, nothing to write home about. ", "We didn't stay for long. It was all a bit of a non-event. No nice views and pretty average service. ", "If you want a couple of boring sandwiches and chocolate brownies whilst looking at the underside of the DLR, this place is perfect. If you want a proper afternoon tea experience, go elsewhere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r522558967", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Completely average- but expensive", "diner_date": " September 2017", "rating_date": "8 September 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "marcm396", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r522558967-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Quite a disappointing experience, given other Hiltons I have stayed at. I had 1 Double gin and tonic which set me back \u00a317.40", "The calamari was basically fried tentacles, and the server (who was very nice and polite) forgot one of our orders, which was a caeser salad. When it came out it had a small amount of dressing and was just bland.", "The restaurant is well lit, very clean and has an ok layout, but it's expensive for what it is and considering it wasn't busy, it took a very long time for the food to come out.", "I can't fault the staff who were very nice, but I think it's let down by bland food and very high prices "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r500144059", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great snacks and breakfast", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "10 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear JohnJampot,", "Thank you so much for your kind words. We are pleased to hear that you enjoyed the moment in our hotel and we appreciate you taking the time to share with feedback with us and other valuable guests. ", "Kind Regards,", "Kestutis V.", "Restaurant Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JohnJampot", "reviewer_origin": ["Letchworth, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "394"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "127"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r500144059-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["The hotel were happy to prepare our kids a snack after a long day out and about. It came quickly and was good food."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r486889643", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Afternoon tea", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "23 May 2017", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "tharanneys", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "10"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r486889643-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Don't Bother! Did not live up to the standard we expect from Hilton.", "19 of us went together; they struggled to after the dietary need of vegetarian and vegan diet.", "The cakes were very small and dry.", "Sandwiches tasted nice but same old boring varieties.", "Good attentive staff particularly the manager was accommodating."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r498948628", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Afternoon Tea", "diner_date": " July 2017", "rating_date": "5 July 2017", "answer_text": ["Dear Phil O,", "Thank you for your valuable feedback. We regret that you were not satisfied on this occasion and apologies for any inconvenience caused. You have my assurances that any shortfall in our service on this occasion is not typical of our usual high standards and I thank you for bringing this to my attention. ", "We are continuously working on our level of service to exceed all of our guest expectations at all time. ", "I hope you will afford us the opportunity of welcoming you back to the Hilton Canary Wharf once again so that we may restore your faith in us. Please feel free to contact Restaurant team or myself so that we can make the necessary arrangements for you. ", "Kind Regards,", "Kestutis V.", "Restaurant Manager"], "reviewer_pseudo": "JonO3329", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r498948628-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Poor service and even poorer afternoon tea. We were presented with sandwiches that were made from cheap bread, the fillings utterly tasteless; we probably could have bought tastier ones in the local supermarket. They forgot to serve the tea with the sandwiches and my daughter had to look for a waiter in order to request they serve us the tea. We were in the downstairs restaurant which had absolutely no atmosphere whatsoever.", " I have advice for anyone thinking of going; DON'T! !"]}
