{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r251967244", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Poorest of poor service. Made worse by relative price!", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "31 January 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jimmypirate", "reviewer_origin": ["Portadown, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "83"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r251967244-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["After a breakfast in a cafe in Enfield that did \u00a30.90p coffee and a breakfast that was exceptional to later arriving to the Hilton Canary Wharf for one has to be considered one of the poorest dining experiences ever, irrelevant of cost! The soup starter was served and a spoon had to be requested in order to eat said soup some 10 minutes wait after getting starter, the medium rare fillet steak was at best warm and very over cooked and another fillet was also only warm! The food was returned slightly eaten to be returned with the same portion of onion rings returned with and the chips for the other were neither taken away or replaced. While I was very hungry and my replaced food was satisfactory the friend accompanying me could not face his as the meal was not corrected. This is worse by the fact we were in he Hilton hotel and not some back street eatery that it seemed like. ", "Very disappointed and now we have to arrange alternative food as the correction to the poor service was not even correct!!", "Such a sad experience of what was started as a luxury experience! ", "I don't know what else to say? I spent the week in Malta in a hotel that cost less than a night here and was much better pleased with the service!!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r261016039", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "The Best!", "diner_date": " March 2015", "rating_date": "22 March 2015", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Allan050651", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "161"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "89"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r261016039-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We came here on a Saturday night with deal package. Three courses each from a limited set menu. Surroundings so very nice and lovely and quiet. We both had the scallops to start. Very tasty but a little on the small side in terms of quantity. My wife had the salmon for main which she loved and reasonable sized portion. I had the beef burgeon which was spectacular. Superb, fresh and a large portion. The sauce was perfect and the mash potatoes the same. I had the the exotic fresh fruit salad for dessert. So many different fruits that really impressed me! The service sometimes was a bit slow but they did apologise for that. Very polite staff. Would love to come back"]}
