{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r231302092", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "BEST BRUNCH EVER!!!", "diner_date": " October 2013", "rating_date": "28 September 2014", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lisa B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r231302092-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["This Review is very late as I was not yet writing reviews on trip advisor. My friends and I had purchased group on vouchers in 2012 for the cinnamon restaurant at Hilton Canary Wharf and the vouchers expired in January 2013. This meant that over the festive season of 2012 we were enjoying brunches on a Sunday morning with family and friends and even got to celebrate my son's and dad's birthday together as a family gathering. The deal was \u00a319 for two adults but you could add children at \u00a36 each at the restaurant. ", "Where do I start? Well the ambiance was fantabulous to say the least, very comfortable furnishings which although classy enough was still very child friendly. The staff could not be more accommodating which is what one would expect from somewhere like the Hilton. They were all so attentive and child friendly. Our party was filled with lots of children and we never once felt the we needed to apologise for this.", "The food? Well certainly the star of the show. The variety of choices for breakfast was amazing but not just variety and quantity but also quality and well prepared. Then there was the choice of meal from the lunch menu which was like a fusion Asian theme and it did not disappoint!", "If it was not for the groupon deal I probably would not have been aware of it and without the deal it would have been far more pricey but based on the quality of food, services and ambience I would gladly pay full price to have brunch here once per month. Unfortunately this morning I rang up to book a table for two adults two kids fro brunch and was told that they no longer do brunches, only breakfast. They don't even do lunches anymore. I was so disappointed to say the least. I guess perhaps they were unable to sustain brunches as that side of Canary wharf is not very busy on weekends and they could not keep doing groupon deals. Shame as I've not been able to find anywhere else in South East to do a brunch as good.", "By the way I've put October 2013 only because they won't allow the date to go back as far as 2012 and I feel it would be an injustice if I didn't write this review even though they no longer do brunches. Thunk we might try their breakfast though and will let you know how that goes."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r203557993", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "The only good thing is the service", "diner_date": " April 2014", "rating_date": "1 May 2014", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Irina V", "reviewer_origin": ["London, England, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "50", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r203557993-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a dinner at the Cinnamon restaurant and that was quite bad, the only great thing was the service.", "Out of 10 course taster menu we only liked lemon sorbet, the rest was just OK. ", "I do not think I would go there any time soon."]}
