{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r151036059", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "I like it.", "diner_date": null, "rating_date": "30 January 2013", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jv27", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "19"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r151036059-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["Look this place is a hotel restaurant, but the hotel is a Hilton in London. it might cost a few pounds more but the service is top notch, the food is very good for a hotel restaurant, and the menu has some good signature dishes.The wine list could be more interesting but it's a hilton they probably buy en masse. Suggest if your local ask for a loyalty card which gets you 15% off every visit, this at least negates some of the vat or tip. The bar food is good too and the burger is cheaper and better than the trendy pub opposite near the dlr. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r148121004", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delicious brunch and value for money", "diner_date": " December 2012", "rating_date": "27 December 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sunnyhand7", "reviewer_origin": ["Crowborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "23"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r148121004-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["We purchased a travel zoo voucher to use at the Cinnamon restaurant at the HIlton in Canary Wharf for \u00a319 to include a cocktail and brunch for two. We managed to book a table for a Saturday just before Christmas and wasn't really expecting too much considering the price. We needn't have worried.", "We were treated to some very good food. The brunch included the choice of two cocktails and included tea, coffee or fruit juices. You were able to choose from a wide variety of hot food with a fresh egg station where you could choose how your eggs or omelette were cooked. All the food here was of a high standard and hot. You were then given the option of choosing one item off the a la carte menu which had sea bass, a sweet potato curry, a chicken dish, roast beef and vegetables, scallops and many more.", "I chose the beef with yorkshire pudding and vegetables which arrived on a hotplate sizzling and cooked to perfection. It was a large piece of sirloin which was delicious, My husband chose the sea bass and vegetables which he said was lovely too.", "We both felt that this deal was brilliant value for money and given the chance would return for another helping!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d1386832", "id_comment": "g186338-d1386832-r145780376", "resto": "Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d1386832-Reviews-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Delicious Creative Food; Service both great and poor", "diner_date": " November 2012", "rating_date": "19 November 2012", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ViewontheHudson", "reviewer_origin": ["New York City, New York"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "136"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Atmosphere", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "40", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d1386832-r145780376-Cinnamon_Restaurant_and_Bar-London_England.html", "content": ["This place has a delicious menu at good prices. I was here with a friend on a Thursday night and the food and service were superb in every way. The sea bass was to die for. So well prepared! Nice choice of dishes with an Indian influence. A number of great choices including attractive vegetarian dishes.", "The next day, Friday, the place was very busy. It took about 15min just to \"prepare\" my table. Although I was quickly served a drink and my dinner order taken quickly, once my meal was served there was no attention from the waiter even though he seated a couple at the next table at one point. Getting a cup of coffee was a chore.", "The bar service was consistently very good, both quick and attentive."]}
